snippet.title: Mums Daily
snippet.description:
Hi Friends,

I am Neethu Johns, a Software Engineer by profession, who is now taking care of my sweet family.

First of all, I would like to thank each of you for taking your valuable time to visit my channel and videos.

 Here, I am making a small attempt to share my own Indian style Recipes,Kids Recipes, My daily house routine, Cleaning tips, Family Vlogs, DIY's etc.

I would like to share my experience as a mum to u Mums!!!!

Please do support me, Like, Share & Subscribe!!

U can get in touch with me via email: mumsdaily85@gmail.com

Please visit my other channel :  Mums Daily Tips & Tricks 
Youtube Link : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrfKsNgUlmTmUBxvB8_32Lw

#mumsdailytips&tricks

Neethu
